* Static imports
* Exception filters
* Auto-property initializers
* Expression bodied members
* Null propagator
* String interpolation
* nameof operator
1 Static import:
	access without specifying a type name 
	using System;
	public double Area
   	{
      		get { return Math.PI * Math.Pow(Radius, 2); }
   	}
	----
	using System;
	using static System.Math;
	public double Area
	{
	      get { return PI * Pow(Radius, 2); }
	}
